{"id":5336,"date":"2026-01-23T03:15:34","date_gmt":"2026-01-23T03:15:34","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.npackpm.com\/?page_id=5336"},"modified":"2026-01-24T02:02:43","modified_gmt":"2026-01-24T02:02:43","slug":"maquina-llenadora-de-desodorantes","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.npackpm.com\/es\/deodorant-filling-machine","title":{"rendered":"M\u00e1quina llenadora de desodorantes"},"content":{"rendered":"<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-page\" data-elementor-id=\"5336\" class=\"elementor elementor-5336\" data-elementor-post-type=\"page\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-656de7b0 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"656de7b0\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-99354b4 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"99354b4\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-15e2db4e elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"15e2db4e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\"> M\u00e1quina autom\u00e1tica de llenado de desodorantes<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2bec6fdf elementor-widget-divider--view-line elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider\" data-id=\"2bec6fdf\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"divider.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-divider\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-divider-separator\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3bc5def7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"3bc5def7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>La m\u00e1quina de llenado de desodorantes Npack es un tipo de equipo de llenado, que se adapta a la tecnolog\u00eda avanzada de llenado en caliente, el proceso de trabajo es t\u00edpicamente de llenado en caliente, la f\u00f3rmula s\u00f3lida se funde, luego se dispensa en el barril de barra vac\u00eda, despu\u00e9s del llenado, una estaci\u00f3n de enfriamiento (t\u00fanel de enfriamiento) lo solidifica antes de tapar. El control preciso del volumen se consigue normalmente con una llenadora de pist\u00f3n, que tambi\u00e9n se acciona mediante un servomotor.<\/p><p>La m\u00e1quina est\u00e1 dise\u00f1ada para cambios r\u00e1pidos entre diferentes tama\u00f1os de envases y l\u00edneas de productos, es f\u00e1cil de operar y limpiar y es adecuada para el llenado de l\u00edquidos calientes o viscosos.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2e6fd310 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"2e6fd310\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-211b2ccb elementor-widget elementor-widget-video\" data-id=\"211b2ccb\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;youtube_url&quot;:&quot;https:\\\/\\\/youtu.be\\\/jo0OqbwteRc&quot;,&quot;show_image_overlay&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;,&quot;image_overlay&quot;:{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https:\\\/\\\/www.npackpm.com\\\/wp-content\\\/uploads\\\/2025\\\/10\\\/2025101510050893.webp&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:2803,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;tube filling and sealing machine&quot;,&quot;source&quot;:&quot;library&quot;},&quot;video_type&quot;:&quot;youtube&quot;,&quot;controls&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"video.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-wrapper elementor-open-inline\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-video\"><\/div>\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-custom-embed-image-overlay\" style=\"background-image: url(https:\/\/www.npack